<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Install PaperTrail</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light dark;
        --bg: #f4f7fb;
        --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
        --card-border: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        --text: #0f172a;
        --muted: #475569;
        --accent: #0a84ff;
        --accent-2: #34c759;
        --chip: rgba(10,132,255,0.12);
        --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          --bg: #0b1020;
          --card: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.78);
          --card-border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
          --text: #f8fafc;
          --muted: #cbd5e1;
          --accent: #4da3ff;
          --accent-2: #30d158;
          --chip: rgba(77,163,255,0.16);
          --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        }
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", "Inter", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(10,132,255,0.18), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(52,199,89,0.12), transparent 25%),
          var(--bg);
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .wrap {
        max-width: 56rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
      }
      .hero {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      }
      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.45rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--chip);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
      }
      .lead {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.03rem;
        max-width: 42rem;
      }
      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.9rem;
        margin-top: 1.4rem;
      }
      a.button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.55rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #5e5ce6);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.95rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(10,132,255,0.28);
      }
      a.secondary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 0.95rem 1.05rem;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
      .panel {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 1rem 1.05rem;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      }
      .label {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      }
      .value {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 650;
        line-height: 1.45;
        word-break: break-word;
      }
      .value code, .technical code {
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 0.92em;
      }
      .steps, .technical {
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
      .steps ol {
        margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .steps li { margin: 0.5rem 0; }
      .technical details {
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
        background: var(--card);
      }
      .technical summary {
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 650;
      }
      .technical p, .technical li {
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .changelog {
        font-size: 1.02rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .subtle {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="eyebrow">PaperTrail · Ad Hoc build</div>
        <h1>Install the latest PaperTrail build</h1>
        <p class="lead">This page is for internal iPhone/iPad testing. If your device is already included in the provisioning profile, install should work in one tap.</p>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="button" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&amp;url=${MANIFEST_URL}">Install on iPhone or iPad</a>
          <a class="secondary" href="${IPA_URL}">Download IPA</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <article class="panel">
          <div class="label">Uploaded</div>
          <div class="value" id="build-upload-time-local">Loading local time…</div>
          <div class="subtle" id="build-upload-time-utc">UTC: ${BUILD_UPLOAD_TIME}</div>
        </article>

        <article class="panel">
          <div class="label">What changed</div>
          <div class="value changelog">${BUILD_CHANGELOG}</div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="panel steps">
        <div class="label">Install notes</div>
        <ol>
          <li>Open this page on the iPhone or iPad you want to test with.</li>
          <li>Tap <strong>Install on iPhone or iPad</strong>.</li>
          <li>If iOS warns about trust/profile/device eligibility, check that the device UDID is included in the Ad Hoc provisioning profile.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="technical">
        <details>
          <summary>Technical details</summary>
          <p>Use this if install fails or you want the raw release links.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Manifest URL: <code>${MANIFEST_URL}</code></li>
            <li>Direct IPA URL: <code>${IPA_URL}</code></li>
            <li>Build uploaded at (UTC): <code>${BUILD_UPLOAD_TIME}</code></li>
            <li>Build uploaded at (ISO): <code>${BUILD_UPLOAD_TIME_ISO}</code></li>
          </ul>
        </details>
      </section>

      <p class="footer">The displayed upload time is automatically converted to your device’s local timezone.</p>
    </main>

    <script>
      (function () {
        var iso = '${BUILD_UPLOAD_TIME_ISO}';
        var localNode = document.getElementById('build-upload-time-local');
        var utcNode = document.getElementById('build-upload-time-utc');
        var parsed = new Date(iso);

        if (!isNaN(parsed.getTime())) {
          localNode.textContent = parsed.toLocaleString(undefined, {
            dateStyle: 'medium',
            timeStyle: 'short'
          });

          utcNode.textContent = 'UTC: ' + parsed.toUTCString().replace('GMT', 'UTC');
        } else {
          localNode.textContent = '${BUILD_UPLOAD_TIME}';
        }
      })();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
